The '''Clear Sector''' was the area of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Radnor/Legends|Radnor]] that was not affected by the planet's deadly bioplague. The [[City/Legends|city]]-state of [[Tacto]] was located in the Clear Sector. The city-state of [[Aubendo]] was located in the [[Isolation Sector]], where the bioplague first struck.

